data.title: The Spirit of British History by National Benzole Company: Very Good Soft cover
data.meta_description: Soft cover - Publicity Arts Ltd. - Condition: Very Good - Not Issued - undated, probably 1950's National Benzolwe Company was formed in 1919 to market motor benzole, a by product of coal carbonization, and blended with petrol as National Benzole mixture. 8 pages inclusive of wrappers, some marking and rusting staples, a scarce publicity publication - The Spirit of British History
